item.content:encoded:
Are you ready for a party? It’s been a while since these princesses went out at a party and they are so excited to finally go out and have some fun! By the way, what do teens wear at parties nowadays? What would you wear, if you were to go out at this killer party tonight? Can you help these princesses get ready and look fabulous? Open their wardrobe and start to mix and match some cute and funky tops with skirts, pants, or shorts and find some trendy accessories. Have fun!

item.content:encoded:
Ice princess in the game is very personalized.Ice princess doesn’t like traditional and conservative long skirts, she likes fashionable shorts. Players can choose clothes with various patterns for ice princess, including beautiful girl soldiers, cats and dogs, stars and butterflies,and so on. In addition, players can also choose different hair styles for ice princess. Snow white hair can reflect the temperament of ice princess more, blue hair can experience the personality of ice princess more, no matter what color of hair, players can enjoy the beautiful game.

item.content:encoded:
You need to help the princess choose accessories, make exquisite flower bags, choose beautiful dresses, and make her the most stunning and beautiful princess ever. Last but not least, you have to help bridesmaids choose dresses. The bridesmaid’s dress is also very important, because the princess hopes that the bridesmaid can also become one of the most beautiful people on the wedding scene..Finally, use the camera to shoot this extraordinary wedding, you can choose different scene pictures to serve as the background image.

item.content:encoded:
The sexy red-haired female celebrity is going to the studio to shoot an advertisement today, but her makeup artist can not rush to the studio in time due to traffic jams. Now, it is time for you to do makeup and take pictures for the female celebrity. Make a complete makeover for the female celebrity at the spa, relax with her in the nail spa, help her choose the right clothes, and create the perfect makeup with cool makeup. The female star thank you very much for your help and give you a signed photo as a gift!
Click to play.

item.content:encoded:
Geisha Glass Skin Routine is a very traditional makeup game, in which you need to apply makeup to a Japanese geisha. Japanese entertainers who perform traditional Japanese artforms, such as traditional dance and singing. They are distinctively characterized by the kimono and the oshiroi makeup they wear. Finally, choose some good-looking accessories for the geisha, such as fans and headwear. Japanese Geisha is very beautiful, come and experience this game!
Click to play.

item.content:encoded:
Summer is here, and the hot weather is unbearable! There is no doubt that everyone hopes that they can spend the whole summer by the sea. Who would refuse white sand beaches and swimming in clear waters? For fashionistas, spending summer by the sea is a great time to wear cute wave dresses, tight shorts and floral tops! The princesses want to become qualified fashionistas, but they need your help. Come and choose suitable summer dresses for the princesses, and finally prepare some beautiful accessories!
Click to play.
